<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Box Model Demo</title>
  <!-- Link to external CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav class="navbar">
    <h1 class="logo">My Website</h1>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <header class="hero">
    <h2>Welcome to the Box Model Example</h2>
    <p>This page demonstrates margins, padding, borders, and background colors.</p>
    <button class="cta-btn">Learn More</button>
  </header>

  <!-- Container with Cards -->
  <section class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Card One</h3>
      <p>This card shows padding inside the border and margin outside.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Card Two</h3>
      <p>Each card has its own margin to create space between elements.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h3>Card Three</h3>
      <p>The background color makes the box model easy to visualize.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2025 My Website | Built with HTML & CSS</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

/* General Reset */
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  line-height: 1.6;
  background-color: #f4f4f9;
}

/* Navigation Bar */
.navbar {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 15px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.navbar .logo {
  margin: 0;
}

.navbar .nav-links {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
}

.navbar .nav-links a {
  color: #fff;
  text-decoration: none;
}

.navbar .nav-links a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Hero Section */
.hero {
  background-color: #e0f7fa;
  border: 2px solid #00796b;
  padding: 30px;
  margin: 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.hero h2 {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.hero p {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.cta-btn {
  background-color: #00796b;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.cta-btn:hover {
  background-color: #004d40;
}

/* Container and Cards */
.container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  padding: 20px;
  justify-content: center;
}

.card {
  background-color: #fff3e0;
  border: 2px solid #ff9800;
  padding: 20px;
  margin: 10px;
  width: 250px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-align: center;
}

.card h3 {
  margin-top: 0;
}

/* Footer */
.footer {
  background-color: #333;
  color: #fff;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 15px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}
